channel.title: Anyway for me to crash my own network
channel.description: I need to crash my own network thats like 5 computers and we have cables through the walls and shit because my SISTER IS PLAYING FUCKING CRYSIS, FUCKING BOTCH NERD, and its crippling my downloads to 10KBS!!! I need to kick this bitch off the network but my router interface is disabled and she will know if I go down and unplug the router...Any ides CMD or something?

item.title: Anyway for me to crash my own network
item.dc:creator: @The_Un-Named The Un-Named
item.description:
@The_Un-Named wrote:

Set up a local ftp server(using filezilla perhaps), disable any throttling on file transfers and transfer several large files over. Always crashes my shitty router and I can only set the maximum transfer speed to something like 2mb/s.

item.title: Anyway for me to crash my own network
item.dc:creator: @Tico135 Tico
item.description:
@Tico135 wrote:

Go to your fuse box/breaker panel and turn off the breaker (or take out the fuse) of the circuit in which she is on. Of course, just act like the power went out. If you have a breaker panel, she’ll go to turn it back on, where you can just unplug her internet connection.
